        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>School Hunger Elimination Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill revises requirements under the National School Lunch Program and the School Breakfast Program of the Department of Agriculture, including by expanding mandatory direct certification of low-income children for free or reduced-price meals.</p>]]>
